#  ▐█▀▀█▄▐█ ▌▐▌▐█·▐█·██ ▪ ██ ▄▄▄▀▀▀█▄   ║║║ ║ ║ ╠╣ ║║  ║╣ ╚═╗
#  ██▄▪▐███ ██▌▐█▌▐█▌▐█▌ ▄▐███▌▐█▄▪▐█  ═╩╝╚═╝ ╩ ╚  ╩╩═╝╚═╝╚═╝
#  ·▀▀▀▀ ▀▀  █▪▀▀▀▀▀▀.▀▀▀ ·▀▀▀  ▀▀▀▀   https://dot.bmilcs.com
#                 YAY INSTALLER [./install-yay]
#────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

source _bm

_tb yay installer
ypath=~/.config/yay/yay

sudo pacman -S --needed git base-devel
git clone https://aur.archlinux.org/yay.git "$ypath"
cd "$ypath"
makepkg -si

